  "title": "Personal Driver cum assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Highlights</strong></p><p>· Car will be provided</p><p>· Not allowed to drive the car back home</p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><p>1. Providing full assistance to Director and family’s including appointment arrangement, personal purchase and payment.</p><p>2. Personal driver to Director and family.</p><p>3. Responsible for car servicing, car maintenance and ensure cleanliness and hygiene of the car at all times.</p><p>4. Any other duties as assigned. (PA)</p><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><p>1. Singaporean & PR only, able to work with Chinese speaker </p><p>2. Valid Class 3 driving license with clean driving record</p><p>3. Neatly presented and professional</p><p>4. Familiar with Singapore roads and safe driving regulations</p><p>5. Prior experience as a personal driver is advantageous</p><p>6. Reliable, punctual, must be able to speak and read Mandarin</p><p>7. Able to work during evenings and on weekends, as required</p><p>8. Immediately available</p><p><br /></p><p>*Salary Negotiable</p>",
